abstract: OCEAN GROVE, N.J., June 26. -- Bishop James N. FitzGerald of St. Louis, President of the Ocean Grove Camp Meeting Association, delivered the "opening sermon" in the Auditorium this morning, his text being "Sanctify Yourselves."
